  <thing id="sDN1009" name="Inflict Light Wounds" description="When laying your hand upon a creature, you channel negative energy that deals 1d8 points of damage +1 point per caster level (maximum +5).\n\nSince undead are powered by negative energy, this spell cures such a creature of a like amount of damage, rather than harming it." compset="Spell" summary="Touch deals 1d8 damage +1/level (max +5).">
