  <thing id="sCORMasLam" name="Master&apos;s Lament" description="This spell strengthens the bond between master and familiar. For the duration of the spell, any damage or magical effect ({i}charm, energy drain{/i}, etc.) taken by the master is also taken by the familiar, and vice versa. If the effect allows a save, both master and familiar roll their saves separately.\n\nThis spell can be cast on either the master or the familiar.\n\n{i}Corruption Cost{/i}: 1d6 points of Charisma damage." compset="Spell" summary="Target and familiar take each other&#146;s damage as well as their own.">
