 hero.child[xDMiMilPho].field[CustDesc].text = field[descript].text
endif]]></eval>
    </thing>
  <thing id="xDSeEnthra" name="Enthralled" description="You are drawn to and fascinated by evil. You no longer have the will to strike it down. Whenever you fight an evil opponent, you always attack at &#150;4 and any damage you do counts only as nonlethal damage." compset="Special" summary="You are drawn to and fascinated by evil.">
    <fieldval field="Value" value="7"/>
    <fieldval field="hName1" value="Evil opponent"/>
