  <thing id="cFBFieExal" name="Fiendish Exaltation" description="At 10th level, you unlock the final secrets buried within your lineage. In addition to the ability boosts you gained from your fiendish heritage, you now gain an additional +1 to Dexterity, Constitution, and Intelligence, and +2 to Strength. You also gain complete immunity to poison, and damage reduction 10/magic." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Deal additional damage to your foes through your spells.">
