  <thing id="cPHDLayHan" name="Lay on Hands" description="Starting at 2nd level, you can lay on hands as a paladin of your class level (see page 44 of the {i}Player&#146;s Handbook{/i}). If you also have paladin levels, these levels stack." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Heal wounds or damage undead with a touch.">
