    </thing>
  <thing id="cPHDSmiTai" name="Smite Taint" description="Beginning at 3rd level, you can smite tainted creatures as a paladin smites evil (see page 44 of the {i}Player&#146;s Handbook{/i}). If you have another smite ability, such as a paladin&#146;s ability to smite evil, you can choose as need dictates to use that power to smite taint instead of the power&#146;s original target.\n\nYou gain additional uses of this power at higher levels (2/day at 6th level and 3/day at 9th level)." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Smite tainted creatures as a paladin smites evil.">
